-- South Africa Should Focus on State Miner, Not Nationalization, Union Says
-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 2010-10-13T08:30:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/south-africa-should-focus-on-state-miner-not-nationalization-union-says.html
Debate in South Africa around the
mining industry should focus on when a state mining company will
be activated rather than nationalization, Senzeni Zokwana, the
president of the National Union of Mineworkers, told reporters
in Johannesburg today.  Debate should be “sober,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
